nodes.name: Analyze idea and generate video metadata
Format AI output for video generation

parameters.content:
## Content discovery
Collect viral content ideas from external sources.
nts/sticky-notes/)

## Data storage
Store viral content ideas in Google Sheets.

## Content selection
Pick one unprocessed idea from Google Sheets.

##  Content analysis
Turn the idea into a title, description, and video prompt.

## Video generation
Send the prompt, wait for the video, and check the result.

## Publishing
Post the video and update the result.

## Setup Guide

**Author:** [GiangxAI](https://www.youtube.com/@giangxai.official)

Follow the steps below to get the workflow running:

Step 1: Copy the [Google Sheets](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AvE7tSFxcIHXN7xLwFNvMrAeI8J3wMPo-cs0TFrPgPA/edit) template  
Create your own copy and connect it to all Google Sheets nodes in the workflow.

Step 2: Configure API credentials  
Add your API keys for the AI model, video generation service, and posting platform in n8n Credentials.

Step 3: Review HTTP Request nodes  
Make sure all video generation and status-check endpoints are correctly configured.

Step 4: Adjust schedules  
Set the Schedule Trigger nodes based on how often you want to generate and publish content.

Step 5: Test with sample data  
Add a few test rows to Google Sheets and run the workflow to verify the full pipeline.

json.input_text: High-angle indoor security camera footage of a modern kitchen, dated October 14, 2025. The room features light grey cabinetry, white countertops, and a dark floor covered in a massive amount of white flour. A woman stands in the center wearing a beige sweatshirt and dark green sweatpants, arms crossed, staring down at a Golden Retriever and an orange tabby cat sitting in the flour. The cat meows up at the woman. She uncrosses her arms and points an accusatory finger at the dog. The Golden Retriever throws his head back in a loud, mournful howl-bark. To the right, a toddler in a yellow shirt bangs on the tray of a white high chair.
